# snipit-multicolor

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/snipit-mc.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/snipit-mc)
[![PyPI downloads](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/snipit-mc.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/snipit-mc/)
